Package: gsDesignCRT
Version: 1.0.1
Title: Group Sequential Design for Cluster Randomized Trials
Authors@R: person(given = "Lee", family = "Ding", email =
          "lee_ding@g.harvard.edu", role = c('aut','cre'))
Description: Derives group sequential cluster randomized trial designs with
    continuous or binary outcomes. Extends the package gsDesign (Anderson, 2024)
    based on methods described in the manuscript "Designing group sequential 
    cluster randomized trials with continuous or binary outcomes" by Lee Ding 
    and Rui Wang.
